ICS for Motorola Bravo (Android 4.0.1 CM9)


Download:
=========

repo init -u git://github.com/CyanogenKobe/android.git -b ics

repo sync


Download RomManager (DELETED IN BUILD)
======================================

mkdir vendor/cyanogen/proprietary
cd vendor/cyanogen && ./get-rommanager


Build:
======

rm -rf out/target

For CM9 branch :
  source build/envsetup.sh && brunch kobe

or for AOSP :
  source build/envsetup.sh && lunch full_kobe-eng
  mka bacon

Use the signed zip to update the defy with the bootmenu recovery, not the ota package !

